  "title": "BEAUTICIAN/SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>We are established beauty wellness centre.We are looking for suitable and commited candidates to join our team.</p><p>We welcomeall races, genders and age groups to apply for this position.</p><p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>-Provide consistent professional beauty treatments to customers, including facial and body therapy, skin care treatments, eyelash extenstion services etc</p><p>-Ensure high level of service standards.</p><p>-Responsible for the maintenance of cleanliness and neatness of the facilities. ( Including replenish of beauty products, towel supplies etc)</p><p>- Able to handle customer queries, facilitate and make proper arrangement for customer appointments.</p><p>-Follow and comply with the instructions given by Duty manager.</p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>-Preferable with ITEC/WSQ certificate</p><p>-Good communication and interpersonal skill</p><p>-Able to commit on weekends/public holidays</p><p>-Able to work long hours and overtime</p><p>-Minimum 2 year of relevant experience</p><p>-Able to withstand body ordour</p><p>-Pleasant personality and hardworking</p><p><u><strong>Benefits</strong></u></p><p>-Attractive salary</p><p>-Attractive bonus</p><p>-Good leadership programme</p>",
